ax-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><br \/>\n<div  style='height:20px' class='hr hr-invisible   avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_image  el_before_av_image '><span class='hr-inner ' ><span class='hr-inner-style'><\/span><\/span><\/div><br \/>\n<div  class='avia-image-container avia_animated_image avia_animate_when_almost_visible pop-up av-styling- av-hover-grow   avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_hr  avia-builder-el-last  avia-align-center '  itemprop=\"image\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\"  ><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><div class='avia-image-overlay-wrap'><a href='https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech.jpg' class='avia_image'  ><img width=\"600\" height=\"600\" class='wp-image-1826 avia-img-lazy-loading-not-1826 avia_image' src=\"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech.jpg\" alt='Rotating Equipment Repair - Power Plant Services (PPS) - Tech' title='Rotating Equipment Repair - Power Plant Services (PPS) - Tech'  itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech.jpg 600w, https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech-80x80.jpg 80w, https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech-36x36.jpg 36w, https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/rotating-equipment-repair-pps-tech-180x180.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/p><\/div><div class=\"flex_column av_two_third  flex_column_div   avia-builder-el-10  el_after_av_one_third  avia-builder-el-last  \" ><p><div  style='padding-bottom:10px; font-size:28px;' class='av-special-heading av-special-heading-h1  blockquote modern-quote  avia-builder-el-11  el_before_av_hr  avia-builder-el-first  av-inherit-size '><h1 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop=\"headline\"  >Field Repair <span class='special_amp'>&amp;<\/span> Machining Services<\/h1><div class='special-heading-border'><div class='special-heading-inner-border' ><\/div><\/div><\/div><br \/>\n<div  style=' margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px;'  class='hr hr-custom hr-left hr-icon-no   avia-builder-el-12  el_after_av_heading  el_before_av_textblock '><span class='hr-inner  inner-border-av-border-thin' style=' width:90%; border-color:#d10202;' ><span class='hr-inner-style'><\/span><\/span><\/div><br \/>\n<section class=\"av_textblock_section \"  itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop=\"text\" ><h2>Power Plant Repair Services&#8217; (PPRS) field repair and machining services can spring into action on-site to address your needs swiftly and effectively<\/h2>\n<p>For jobs that require extensive field services during a planned or forced outage, Power Plant Services\u2019 team of certified field machinists can arrive on-site with all the tooling, machinery, and safety measurements to support your outage.<\/p>\n<p>It is our policy at Power Plant Services to exceed customer\u2019s expectations through consistent safety, quality, on-time delivery, and continual improvement of our service and repair products. Our team members have the repair experience needed to complete the scope of work, along with best practices aligned with industry and OEM guidelines.<\/p>\n<p>With this in mind, PPS takes extensive care of our machinery and tooling as we understand the importance of organization and cleanliness on the job-site. Our Power Plant Services field machining and repair services team will review and examine tooling required to complete the scope of work, as well as keep duplicates of all tooling sets to assure there is no tooling delay.<\/p>\n<h3>PPRS Field repair equipment includes but is not limited to:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Large Turning Devices<\/li>\n<li>Portable Low Speed Balancing Machine<\/li>\n<li>Boring Bars From 2 \u00bc\u201d to 12\u201d in Diameter<\/li>\n<li>Portable Vertical Turning Lathe<\/li>\n<li>Portable Horizontal Mills Up to 24\u201d Long<\/li>\n<li>Portable Horizontal Boring Machine<\/li>\n<li>Automatic Bore Welder<\/li>\n<li>Flange Facing Machines<\/li>\n<li>Hydraulic Power Pack Units<\/li>\n<li>Small, Medium &amp; Large Knee Mills<\/li>\n<li>PPS\u2019 Portable Field Equipment includes:<\/li>\n<li>20\u2032 Container<\/li>\n<li>Surface Grinder<\/li>\n<li>Engine Lathe<\/li>\n<li>Milling Machine<\/li>\n<li>Drill Press<\/li>\n<li>Punch Press<\/li>\n<li>Portable Lathe<\/li>\n<li>Portable Balance Machine<\/li>\n<li>Tool Trailers<\/li>\n<li>Lamina Drills<\/li>\n<li>Stationary Journal Machine<\/li>\n<li>Fully Stock Portable Machine shop<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Field repair services (Field Machining, Field Welding) includes but not limited to:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>FSM Turbine Parts Manufacturing<\/li>\n<li>Turbine rotor repairs (Blade, seal replacement, journal repairs)<\/li>\n<li>Rotor weld repairs<\/li>\n<li>Casing weld repairs<\/li>\n<li>Diaphragms repairs<\/li>\n<li>Dynamic balance<\/li>\n<li>Sole plate<\/li>\n<li>Boiler feed pump barrel restoration<\/li>\n<li>Torque convertor<\/li>\n<li>Gearbox inspection and repairs<\/li>\n<li>Vale seat replacement<\/li>\n<li>Robot welding<\/li>\n<li>Hight valve weld and machining<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Field Service capabilities include:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Steam Turbines\n<ul>\n<li>Major Overhauls<\/li>\n<li>Minor Overhauls<\/li>\n<li>Valves<\/li>\n<li>Packing and Seal Installation<\/li>\n<li>Turbine Retrofits and Upgrades<\/li>\n<li>Alignment<\/li>\n<li>On-Site Semi-Automatic Welding<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Gas Turbines\n<ul>\n<li>Major Overhauls<\/li>\n<li>Minor Overhauls<\/li>\n<li>Generator (major, minor, robotic)<\/li>\n<li>Hot Gas Path Inspection<\/li>\n<li>Combustion Inspection<\/li>\n<li>Seal Installation<\/li>\n<li>On-Site Semi-Automatic Welding<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Balance of Plant\n<ul>\n<li>Boiler Feed Pump<\/li>\n<li>Auxiliary Equipment<\/li>\n<li>Critical Control Valve Inspection<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Power Plant Services continues to expand our on-site capabilities to ensure a smooth transition from outage to power production without the need to ship any components to our repair shops. Additionally, we are continuously expanding equipment that currently includes, but is not limited to, Fully Equipped Portable Machine Shop.<\/p>\n<h3>Contact PPS today at <a href=\"tel: +17083458600\">(708) 345-8600<\/a> or send us a message to explore how we can support your immediate or upcoming project needs.<\/h3>\n<\/div><\/section><\/p><\/div>\n\n<div  class='avia-button-wrap avia-button-center  avia-builder-el-14  el_after_av_section  avia-builder-el-last ' ><a href='https:\/\/ppsvcs.com\/parts-and-services-quote-request\/' class='avia-button avia-button-fullwidth  avia-font-color-theme-color av-icon-on-hover avia-icon_select-yes-right-icon avia-color-custom '  style='background-color:#0f3e96; ' ><span class='avia_iconbox_title' >REQUEST A QUOTE<\/span><span class='avia_button_icon avia_button_icon_right' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='\ue83c' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'><\/span><div class='av-button-description av-button-description-below'><p>Power Plant Services is always ready to meet the need of our customers, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days of the year.<\/p>\n<\/div><span class='avia_button_background avia-button avia-button-fullwidth avia-color-custom' style='background-color:#d10202;'><\/span><\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":367,"menu_order":2,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":""},"_links":{"self":[{"hr